# azure_ad/

Azure AD SSO client。對齊 `docs/Design-Base/90-third-party-service/04-sso-azure-ad.md` + `01-client-design.md`。

## 結構

| 檔 | 用途 |
| --- | --- |
| `client.py` | `AzureAdClient` — httpx async,timeout / retry 對齊 client-design |
| `schemas.py` | Microsoft Graph response schema |
| `errors.py` | `AzureAdError` 與子類(對齊「錯誤轉換契約」) |
| `__init__.py` | public exports |

## 使用

於 `app/main.py` 的 `lifespan` 建立、dispose:

```python
app.state.azure_ad_client = AzureAdClient(
    client_id=settings.AZURE_AD_CLIENT_ID,
    tenant_id=settings.AZURE_AD_TENANT_ID,
    secret=settings.AZURE_AD_CLIENT_SECRET,
)
yield
await app.state.azure_ad_client.aclose()
```

